title: LaTeX font notes

Fonts are weird in [[LaTeX]]

Controlling section font sizes, etc. using the `titlesec` package

```
\titleformat{\section}
  {\normalfont\sectionfont\large}{}{0pt}{}
\titleformat{\subsection}
  {\normalfont\sectionfont\small}{}{0pt}{}
```

